sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant API
    participant NLPService
    participant GeminiAI
    participant Database
    
    User->>Frontend: Types "biryani rahul 500"
    Frontend->>API: POST /parse (text, group_id)
    API->>NLPService: parse_expense(text)
    
    alt Regex Match Found
        NLPService-->>NLPService: Extract details
    else Complex Input
        NLPService->>GeminiAI: Parse Request
        GeminiAI-->>NLPService: Structured JSON
    end
    
    NLPService-->>NLPService: Categorize & Detect Person
    NLPService-->>API: Parsed Expense Object
    API-->>Frontend: Confirmation Preview
    
    Frontend->>User: Show Preview (Confirm?)
    User->>Frontend: Clicks Confirm
    Frontend->>API: POST /expenses (save)
    API->>Database: INSERT expense
    Database-->>API: Success
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK
    Frontend-->>User: "Expense Added!"
